<p class="bloglist"> For a colourful history on the U.S.-Canada Softwood Lumber Trade Disputes and the subsequent “morning wood”, read Tabatha Southey’s recent column <i>Explaining the endless softwood saga to our extraterrestrial neighbours</i>.
